least squares line:
https://www.varsitytutors.com/hotmath/hotmath_help/topics/line-of-best-fit
avg_Y
avg_X
Table of xi-avgX, yi-avgY, (xi-avgX)(yi-avgY), (xi-avgX)^2
slope = SUM[(xi-avgX)(yi-avgY)] / SUM[(xi-avgX)^2]
b (intercept) = avgY - slope * avgX
draw the line yi = (slope) xi + b
plot the points overlaid on graph: scatter plot


